  "text": "In this section, we present our experimental results for evaluating the performances of CSeg'18 to that of CSeg'17 using our proposed evaluation metric. We used the eBay test dataset [CITATION_1] for our experiments. This dataset consists of four object-classes: cars, dresses, pot glasses and shoes. Each of these classes is again divided into 11 colour-classes. In each colour class of an object, there are 12 images. Therefore, the dataset has in total = 4 × 11 × 12 = 528 images. The foreground object of an image determines its object-class and colour of that object determines its colour-class.",
